    <item>
      <title>NETGEAR 推出全新 WiFi 7 產品線，Orbi RBE370 系列路由器與 A9000 接收器雙登場</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/08/01/netgear-wifi-7-2/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=netgear-wifi-7-2</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/08/01/netgear-wifi-7-2/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>Lawton</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Aug 2025 13:02:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>家居無線</category>
      <category>路由器</category>
      <category>NETGEAR</category>
      <category>WiFi 7</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1319174</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;NETGEAR 宣佈推出全新 WiFi 7 網絡裝置產品，當中包括主打入門高效能的 Orbi RBE370 Mesh 路由器系列，以及專為筆電升級而設的 Nighthawk A9000 WiFi 7 USB 接收器，進一步滿足家居用戶及玩家對超高速穩定網絡的需求。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0367-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0367-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0367-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Orbi RBE370：全方位 WiFi 7 Mesh 網狀網絡方案&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RBE370 採用雙頻 WiFi 7 Mesh 架構，內建 1.5GHz 四核心處理器，配備 4-Stream 傳輸技術，提供最高 3600 Gbps 傳輸速度，支援 Multi-Link Operation（MLO）功能，大幅減少幹擾並提升連接穩定性。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0356-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0356-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0356-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0341-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0341-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0341-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0340-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0340-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0340-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;主機型號 RBE371 提供 2.5G WAN 埠，支援現今主流光纖或寬頻方案。衞星裝置（RBE370）亦備有 2 組 2.5G LAN 埠，可同時供應最多 70 部設備連線。無論是 8K 串流、遠端工作、AR/VR 應用，皆能應對自如。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NETGEAR 特別加入自家專利天線設計，實現 360 度訊號覆蓋，強化穿牆與全屋接收能力，並針對家居裝潢設計採用隱藏式天線外觀，兼顧性能與美觀。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0381-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0381-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0381-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲在現場實試，配合 NETVIGATOR 寬頻服務，無線 WiFi 實測上到 1456Mbps 速度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;同場加映：旗艦級 NETGEAR Nighthawk RS600 Wi-Fi 7 路由器&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;同場更加映 RS600 系列的展示，想 WiFi 傳輸速度更快的朋友，可選購這款更高階的路由器，支援 WiFi 7 最高無線速度可達 18000Mbps。現場就實測到它的連線速度達到 3233.41Mbps。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1319192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0357-1-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="713" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0357-1-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0357-1-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1319193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0359-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="713" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0359-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0359-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0379-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0379-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0379-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0380-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0380-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0380-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲這部路由器與 NETVIGATOR 寬頻服務結合，在現場實測無線 WiFi 上網速度達 3233.41Mbps。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;另一款新產品 A9000 為 USB 3.0 規格的 WiFi 7 接收器，內建 BE6500 三頻技術，適合用家為舊款手提電腦升級，支援最高傳輸率與 WiFi 7 路由器配對使用，適合高畫質串流與線上遊戲。需留意 A9000 只支援 Windows 11 系統，用戶需確認裝置規格以發揮其最大潛能。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0345-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0345-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0345-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0350-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0350-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0350-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319182" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0352-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0352-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0352-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;NETGEAR Armor 與 Orbi App：安全與簡易安裝兼備&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RBE370 內建 NETGEAR Armor 網絡防護功能，由 Bitdefender 提供技術支援，涵蓋 VPN、惡意程式防護、擴展保養及專屬技術支援。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0373-694x431.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="431" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0373-694x431.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0373-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0374-694x403.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="403" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0374-694x403.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0374.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;另一方面用戶只需透過 Orbi App 便可完成路由器設定，簡化安裝程序。而且 App 內可顯示路由器狀況，也可進行各種設定。&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0371-694x427.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0371-694x427.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0371.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0372-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0372-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0372.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;限時優惠：半價換購、$500 電子禮券、免費升級家電&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;NETGEAR 聯同 csl 與網上行推出兩大限時優惠&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NETGEAR 與 CSL 將會於是次產品發佈會上推出 2 大限時優惠，優惠 1 是凡購買指定支援 WiFi 7 手機/平板/PlayStation 主機即可半價換購指定型號 Wi-Fi7 路由器，而指定型號為 NETGEAR 兩款旗艦級路由器、分別為 OrbiWiFi 7 Mesh RBE970 系列主機 (RBE971S) 以及 Nighthawk Smart Router RS600。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0366-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0366-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_0366-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;購買指定手機/平板/PlayStation 主機，即可半價換購 WiFi 7 路由器&lt;br /&gt;
RBE971S 主機（原價 $7680，半價 $3840）&lt;br /&gt;
RBE970 外部衞星（原價 $6980，半價 $3490）&lt;br /&gt;
Nighthawk Smart Router RS600（原價 $3780，半價 $1890）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;購買 NETGEAR 路由器並成功申請網上行寬頻，即送：&lt;br /&gt;
$500 csl 電子現金券&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MobiWarm 智能溫控咖啡壺 MWCM-A01-S（價值 $798）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;此外，購買指定 WiFi 7 路由器系列（如 RBE370）更可，半價換購 Multi-Gig Switch（MS105 / MS308），升級全屋 2.5G 多重連接能力。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
